an2.jpg\" alt=\"Coogan\" />Steve Coogan on his early days on TV<span class=\"gvl3-icon-wrapper\"><span class=\"gvl3-icon gvl3-icon-invert-watch\"> Watch</span></span><span class=\"av-time\">04:39</span></a>\r\n\r\n\t\t</li>\r\n\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t\t  \t\t\t\t  \t\t\t\t\t  \t\t\t\t\t  \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\t\t\r\n\r\n\r\n\t\t\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>\r\n\t<a class=\"story\" rel=\"published-1382718666413\" href=\"/arts/0/24672968\"><img src=\"http://news.bbcimg.co.uk/media/images/70718000/jpg/_70718593_jimi_in_montagu_place_w1.jpg\" alt=\"Jimi Hendrix in London W1\" />When Jimi Hendrix impressed McCartney<span class=\"gvl3-icon-wrapper\"><span class=\"gvl3-icon gvl3-icon-invert-watch\"> Watch</span></span><span class=\"av-time\">02:46</span></a>\r\n\r\n\t\t</li>\r\n\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t\t  \t\t\t\t  \t\t\t\t\t  \t\t\t\t\t  \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\t\t\r\n\r\n\r\n\t\t\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>\r\n\t<a class=\"story\" rel=\"published-1383332425056\" href=\"/arts/0/24779693\"><img src=\"http://news.bbcimg.co.uk/media/images/71038000/jpg/_71038038_sayingfarewell-detail.jpg\" alt=\"Saying Farewell\" />How the V&amp;A became a Chinese landscape<span class=\"gvl3-icon-wrapper\"><span class=\"gvl3-icon gvl3-icon-invert-watch\"> Watch</span></span><span class=\"av-time\">03:45</span></a>\r\n\r\n\t\t</li>\r\n\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t\t  \t\t\t\t  \t\t\t\t\t  \t\t\t\t\t  \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\t\t\r\n\r\n\r\n\t\t\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>\r\n\t<a class=\"story\" rel=\"published-1381845186528\" href=\"/arts/0/24536773\"><img src=\"http://news.bbcimg.co.uk/media/images/70492000/jpg/_70492919_tartt.jpg\" alt=\"Donna Tartt\" />Donna Tartt reads from The Goldfinch<span class=\"gvl3-icon-wrapper\"><span class=\"gvl3-icon gvl3-icon-invert-watch\"> Watch</span></span><span class=\"av-time\">01:03</span></a>\r\n\r\n\t\t</li>\r\n\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t\t  \t\t\t\t  \t\t\t\t\t  \t\t\t\t\t  \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\t\t\r\n\r\n\r\n\t\t\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>\r\n\t<a class=\"story\" rel=\"published-1382435581777\" href=\"http://www